defaultommittee’s inquiry into Heat and are pleased to submit our response for consideration
default.  We have focussed on space and water heating as the areas most covered by our members, and also which make-up the vast bulk of heat demand.  
defaultIn compiling this submission, we have consulted with our members by circulating an early draft version which was discussed through an online webinar.
